videos.headline: Fitzgerald bursts downfield for 74-yard TD
videos.description: Mississippi State QB Nick Fitzgerald opens up the scoring by racing for a 74-yard touchdown, giving the Bulldogs the lead over Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Texas A&M forces red zone interception
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald pass intercepted by Nick Harvey

videos.headline: Mississippit State QB uses quick reaction to catch the snap and get the 1st down
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald run for 17 yds to the TexAM 6 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Mississippi State extends lead with 2-yard TD run
videos.description: Mississippi State running back Aeris Williams easily gets into the end zone for a two-yard touchdown run to give the Bulldogs a two-score lead over Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Knight's 19-yard TD run gets Aggies on the board
videos.description: Needing a spark down 14-0, Trevor Knight takes off with open field and dives into the end zone for the Texas A&M touchdown. He would then head off to the locker room with pain in his shoulder after the play.

videos.headline: Texas A&M QB Trevor Knight heads to locker room with injury
videos.description: Texas A&M QB Trevor Knight heads to locker room with injury

videos.headline: Fitzgerald finds Ross for 60-yard TD
videos.description: Mississippi State's Nick Fitzgerald throws a pass to Fred Ross complete down the sideline for a 60-yard touchdown to maintain its lead over Texas A&M.

videos.headline: N. Fitzgerald pass,to F. Ross for 7 yds for a TD,
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald pass complete to Fred Ross for 7 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Knight goes down injured again for A&M
videos.description: After being dragged down on a scramble, Trevor Knight stays down with an arm injury. He would be taken to the sidelines and has not returned for Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Aggies get 92-yard punt return TD heading into halftime
videos.description: With just seconds remaining in the first half, Christian Kirk takes the punt and goes 92 yards the other way to the house for his third return touchdown in the last two games for Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Mark McLaurin delivers the huge hit on the Texas A&M QB
videos.description: Jake Hubenak sacked by Mark McLaurin for a loss of 4 yards to the MisSt 9

videos.headline: Mississippi State defense forces a turnover
videos.description: Jake Hubenak sacked by Johnathan Calvin for a loss of 2 yards to the TexAM 48 Jake Hubenak fumbled, forced by Johnathan Calvin, recovered by MisSt Braxton Hoyett ,

videos.headline: Wilson's awesome INT in the end zone keeps Aggies close
videos.description: With Mississippi State looking to go up three scores, Donovan Wilson makes the remarkable interception in the back of the end zone to deny the Bulldogs and keep the Aggies down only 14.

videos.headline: Texas A&M strikes back with 54-yard TD pass to Kirk
videos.description: Texas A&M continues its comeback in Starkville when Jake Hubenak goes deep to Christian Kirk for a 54-yard touchdown to bring the Aggies' deficit down to 28-21.

videos.headline: Mississippi State pulls off upset of No. 4 Texas A&M
videos.description: Mississippi State extends its lead when Nick Fitzgerald fights through tackles to find the end zone to  get the Bulldogs thinking upset with a 35-21 lead late in the fourth quarter.

videos.headline: J. Hubenak pass,to J. Reynolds for 4 yds for a TD
videos.description: Jake Hubenak pass complete to Josh Reynolds for 4 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Mississippi State defense forces a game winning interception
videos.description: Jake Hubenak pass intercepted Mark McLaurin return for no gain to the 50 yard line

videos.headline: Mississippi State upsets No. 4 Texas A&M
videos.description: Nick Fitzgerald throws two touchdown passes and rushes for another two scores as Mississippi State defeats No. 4 Texas A&M 35-28 to hand the Aggies their second loss of the season.
